<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Ashy" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Ashy,</orth> ash-coloured, pale: <cit><quote>anger ashy-pale,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ven 76" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 76</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>dying eyes gleam'd forth their a. lights,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1378" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1378</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a. pale,</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 1378" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 1378</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>a timely parted ghost, of a. semblance,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.162" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 162</bibl></cit>.
